ZH: 在这个工厂里，车间是制造产品的地方。
EN: In this factory, the workshop is where the products are made.

ZH: 车间里的机器很吵，需要戴耳塞保护听力。
EN: The machines in the workshop are very loud, so ear plugs are needed to protect hearing.

ZH: 我每天都要去车间工作，完成生产任务。
EN: I have to go to the workshop every day to complete production tasks.

ZH: 这个车间里有很多员工，大家合作得很好。
EN: There are many employees in this workshop, and everyone works well together.

ZH: 车间里的空气很不好，需要增加通风设备。
EN: The air in the workshop is not good, so ventilation equipment needs to be added.

ZH: 请把这批货物送到车间里，我们需要进行检验。
EN: Please deliver this batch of goods to the workshop for inspection.

ZH: 车间的工作台上摆满了各种工具和材料。
EN: The workbench in the workshop is filled with various tools and materials.

ZH: 车间里的灯光很暗，需要更换新的灯泡。
EN: The lighting in the workshop is very dim and needs to be replaced with new light bulbs.

ZH: 这座车间是按照安全标准设计的，确保员工的安全。
EN: This workshop is designed according to safety standards to ensure the safety of employees.

ZH: 车间的地面很滑，需要铺设防滑垫。
EN: The floor of the workshop is slippery and needs non-slip mats to be laid.

ZH: 我们需要扩建车间的面积，以容纳更多的生产设备。
EN: We need to expand the area of the workshop to accommodate more production equipment.

ZH: 车间内大家都在有序地工作，井然有序。
EN: Everyone in the workshop is working in an organized and orderly manner.

ZH: 车间里的工作环境需要改善，以提高生产效率。
EN: The working environment in the workshop needs to be improved to increase production efficiency.

ZH: 车间的工作人员正在进行设备维护，确保设备正常运行。
EN: The workshop staff are performing equipment maintenance to ensure that the equipment is running properly.

ZH: 请在车间内佩戴安全帽和手套，以确保工作安全。
EN: Please wear a safety helmet and gloves in the workshop to ensure work safety.

ZH: 车间里散发出浓浓的油漆味道，需要增加通风设备。
EN: There is a strong smell of paint in the workshop, so additional ventilation equipment is needed.

ZH: 车间的工作时间是从早上八点到下午五点。
EN: The working hours in the workshop are from 8:00 am to 5:00 pm.

ZH: 车间内的零件堆放地方需要整理，以便更容易取用。
EN: The storage area for parts in the workshop needs to be organized for easier access.

ZH: 这座车间拥有先进的生产设备，使生产更高效。
EN: This workshop has advanced production equipment that makes production more efficient.
